================================================================================
Third-party software
================================================================================

IcontainU is a graphical front-end for Apple's `container` and does not bundle a
container runtime. It builds on, links against, and interoperates with the
following projects. Portions of IcontainU adapt patterns and behaviors from
Apple's `container` command-line interface.

